OL,3,CEx-wife admits 'horrible' messages to
OL,4,Cdrug dealer days before fatal attack
OL,6,FSam Blackledge reports from the scene
OL,7,Fof an acid attack in Plymouth
OL,9,FThe ex-wife of a Plymouth drug dealer
OL,10,Fwho owed hundreds of thousands of
OL,11,Fpounds to his bosses has admitted to
OL,12,Fsending 'horrible messages' to her
OL,13,Fformer spouse just four days before a
OL,14,Ffatal acid attack.
OL,16,FDanny Cahalane was targeted at his
OL,17,Fhome in Lipson Road on 21 February
OL,18,F2025 and later died in hospital.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
